text:
[Verse]
Late night kitchen callin
Fridge light glowing bright
Craving something sweet
Cereal just might

[Verse 2]
Open up the cabinet
Cookies stare at me
Milk right on the side
Perfect harmony

[Chorus]
Midnight snack attack
Can't hold myself back
Chomp and crunch and bite
Feast in the moonlight

[Verse 3]
Ice cream in the freezer
Spoon in hand I'm set
Flavors swirl together
Yet I'm not done yet

[Verse 4]
Popcorn in the corner
Microwave delight
Salty mixed with butter
Best part of the night

[Chorus]
Midnight snack attack
Can't hold myself back
Chomp and crunch and bite
Feast in the moonlight
title: Midnight Snack Attack
